name: Cloud City Sabacc
Lore: 'Sabacc variant popular among the miners. Ugnaughts and chief administrators of Bespin''s city in the clouds.',
Text: 'Requirements: a gambler, thief or smuggler on Cloud City.Wild cards (1-6): Lando and Weather Vane.Clone cards: Locations and Ugnaughts. (Gamblers may use clone cards as zeroes.)Stakes: One starfighter, weapon or device.',
